Fixed Width: Blocks of content will be the same fixed width.
Launching fixed width on small screen : site will zoom out, or render at fixed resolution, possibly ruinign the ux.
Fluid Layout, Liquid Layout: define space and width percentages
Height, Width, Margin, and Padding percentages

Media Queries: retrieve device information in CSS
@ media only screen and (min-width: 768px)
@ media only screen and (max width: 320px) and (min-width: 320px)
ex. unfloat elements in media query:
@media only screen and (max-width: 480px) {
    .article {
        float: none;
        width: auto;
    }
}

Adaptive Design
developers set media queries at widths responding to specific devices in portrait and landscape